
```sql
SELECT rrp.page_code 
FROM FIDATAADM.RIXML_RECEIVER_PAGE RRP
INNER JOIN FIDATAADM.PUB_TYPE_ATTRIBUTE_VALUE PTAV ON PTAV.ID=RRP.PUBLICATION_TYPE_CATEGORY_ID
INNER JOIN FIDATAADM.PUBLICATION_TYPE_ATTRIBUTE PTA ON PTA.PUBTYPE_ATTR_VAL_ID=PTAV.ID
INNER JOIN FIDATAADM.PUBLICATION_TYPE PT ON PT.ID=PTA.PUBLICATION_TYPE_ID
INNER JOIN FIDATAADM.PUBLICATION PUB ON PUB.PUBLICATION_TYPE_ID=PT.ID
```

To introduce the US Debt requirement, we need to make the following changes:

1. Add a new column `IS_US_DEBT` to the PUBLICATION table to identify US Debt content.
2. Update the query to include a check for the `IS_US_DEBT` column.
3. Modify the CASE statement in the SELECT clause to handle the different Bloomberg class assignments based on US Debt vs non-US Debt content.

Here's the updated query:

```sql
SELECT rrp.page_code,
       CASE
           WHEN PTAV.ATTRIBUTE_VALUE = 'Credit' AND PUB.IS_US_DEBT = 'Y' THEN
               CASE LOWER(COALESCE(phtv.tvalue, 'english'))
                   WHEN 'english' THEN 4  -- US Debt Credit 360 English
                   WHEN 'french' THEN 13 -- US Debt Credit 360 French
               END
           ELSE
               CASE LOWER(COALESCE(phtv.tvalue, 'english'))
                   WHEN 'english' THEN 1  -- Markets 360 & non-US Debt Credit 360
                   WHEN 'chinese' THEN 2  -- Chinese content
                   WHEN 'japanese' THEN 3 -- Japanese content
                   WHEN 'french' THEN 12 -- French Markets 360
               END
       END as bbg_class
FROM FIDATAADM.RIXML_RECEIVER_PAGE RRP
INNER JOIN FIDATAADM.PUB_TYPE_ATTRIBUTE_VALUE PTAV ON PTAV.ID=RRP.PUBLICATION_TYPE_CATEGORY_ID
INNER JOIN FIDATAADM.PUBLICATION_TYPE PT ON PT.ID=PTAV.PUBLICATION_TYPE_ID
INNER JOIN FIDATAADM.PUBLICATION PUB ON PUB.PUBLICATION_TYPE_ID=PT.ID
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT PH.ID ID, PH.PUBLICATION_ID PHTV_PUB_ID, PH.TAG_VALUE TVALUE
    FROM FIDATAADM.PUBLICATION_HAS_TAG_VALUE PH
    INNER JOIN FIDATAADM.TAG_TYPE TT
    ON TT.ID=PH.TAG_TYPE_ID AND TT.COLUMN_NAME='bnpp_language'
) PHTV ON PHTV.PHTV_PUB_ID=PUB.ID
WHERE PUB.ID='377933';
```
